---

## Semantic Checks

| Code | Name | What it catches |
|---|---|---|
| SC-01 | `UNKNOWN_ACTION` | Action not in the AWS mock dictionary |
| SC-02 | `BAD_ARN` | Resource doesn't start with `arn:` and isn't `*` |
| SC-03 | `DUPLICATE_STMT` | Exact duplicate (role + action + resource + effect) |
| SC-04 | `CONFLICT_EFFECT` | Same triple but ALLOW vs DENY clash |
| SC-05 | `TYPE_MISMATCH` | `mfa` not TRUE/FALSE, `time` not numeric, [ip](file:///home/manthankhawse/cd-cp/src/semantic.c#99-109) not inet addr |
| SC-06 | `EMPTY_POLICY` | Zero statements after successful parse |

---

## Exit Codes

| Code | Meaning |
|---|---|
| `0` | Syntactically and semantically valid |
| `1` | Syntax / parse failure |
| `2` | Semantic failure |

---

