[Error 1] line 8    [UNKNOWN_ACTION]   SC-01: Unknown AWS action "fakeservice:DoStuff"
[Error 2] line 13   [BAD_ARN]          SC-02: Malformed ARN "not-an-arn-at-all"
[Error 3] line 37   [TYPE_MISMATCH]    SC-05: mfa expects TRUE/FALSE, got "yes"
[Error 4] line 43   [TYPE_MISMATCH]    SC-05: time expects numeric, got "midnight"
[Error 5] line 49   [TYPE_MISMATCH]    SC-05: ip expects IPv4 address, got "my-office"
[Error 6] line 22   [DUPLICATE_STMT]   SC-03: Duplicate ALLOW for Auditor/cloudtrail
[Error 7] line 31   [CONFLICT_EFFECT]  SC-04: DENY conflicts with ALLOW for DevOps/s3:PutObject
```
